  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic Tibial Tray CFD Credibility Assessment (NC-4 Clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for a finite-element and CFD model predicting contact stress and micromotion at the tibial tray–bone interface for a cementless total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict relative interface micromotion under physiological gait loading at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels. Decision: Accepted.",
